WEBVTT

00:01.267 --> 00:03.702
♪

00:03.704 --> 00:07.606
<i>It doesn't seem that my</i>
<i>new role as a princess</i>

00:07.608 --> 00:17.016
I am tirek! And I will take what
should've been mine long ago!

00:17.018 --> 00:20.152
With each passing moment, he
grows stronger still.

00:20.154 --> 00:22.788
And I know just the princess
who can stop him.

00:22.790 --> 00:25.357
I'm afraid I must call in
another to stop tirek.

00:25.359 --> 00:28.160
Oh ho! You're talking
about me I presume.

00:28.162 --> 00:30.696
Haven't you girls just
learned so much!

00:30.698 --> 00:32.498
And there's something
interesting about the sections

00:32.500 --> 00:35.801
Each of you received
something from the pony

00:35.803 --> 00:37.469
Whose life you helped change.

00:38.538 --> 00:41.407
There's still one key
missing: My element.

00:41.409 --> 00:46.078
Join me, discord and
reclaim your greatness.

00:46.080 --> 00:48.547
<i>Luna: Discord has betrayed</i>
<i>the ponies of equestria</i>

00:48.549 --> 00:50.582
<i>And joined forces with tirek.</i>

00:50.584 --> 00:54.386
<i>There is no doubt that tirek</i>
<i>is after alicorn magic.</i>

00:54.388 --> 00:57.056
We must rid ourselves
of our magic

00:57.058 --> 00:59.792
Before tirek has the chance
to steal it from us.

00:59.794 --> 01:01.126
<i>(gasp)</i>

01:01.128 --> 01:05.364
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:05.366 --> 01:07.366
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

01:07.368 --> 01:10.569
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

01:10.571 --> 01:12.738
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

01:12.740 --> 01:14.673
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

01:14.675 --> 01:17.076
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

01:17.078 --> 01:18.077
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

01:18.079 --> 01:20.345
<i>♪ a beautiful heart</i>

01:20.347 --> 01:27.453
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

01:27.455 --> 01:30.522
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

01:30.524 --> 01:33.659
♪

01:40.200 --> 01:43.202
<i>Luna: Tirek is set on</i>
<i>possessing alicorn magic.</i>

01:43.204 --> 01:46.338
When he comes for us, we cannot
have what he is looking for.

01:47.373 --> 01:50.409
I'm more than willing to do
my part and give up my magic.

01:50.411 --> 01:54.580
Our magic cannot just
disappear into thin air.

01:54.582 --> 01:56.882
Somepony must keep it safe.

01:56.884 --> 01:59.485
That somepony is
you, twilight.

01:59.487 --> 02:02.821
We do not believe
that tirek is aware

02:02.823 --> 02:06.158
That a fourth alicorn princess
exists in equestria.

02:06.160 --> 02:08.160
If we transfer our
magic to you,

02:08.162 --> 02:10.462
Tirek will not know
where it has gone.

02:10.464 --> 02:12.898
Do you understand what
we're asking of you?

02:12.900 --> 02:16.535
Yes. It's just I'm only now
learning how to control

02:16.537 --> 02:19.404
My own alicorn magic. To
take on even more...

02:19.406 --> 02:22.608
Twilight, you represent
the element of magic.

02:22.610 --> 02:25.777
If there is anypony who
can do this, it's you.

02:27.413 --> 02:29.915
Taking on this task will be one
of the most difficult things

02:29.917 --> 02:32.818
But with the help
of my friends...

02:32.820 --> 02:34.920
I'm sorry, princess twilight,

02:34.922 --> 02:37.789
But you must keep your
new abilities a secret.

02:37.791 --> 02:40.826
I fear that your friends being
aware of your new power

02:40.828 --> 02:42.895
Could put them at great risk.

02:42.897 --> 02:46.565
Do you still think you can
take on this responsibility?

02:46.567 --> 02:49.801
This is the role I am meant to
play as a princess of equestria.

02:49.803 --> 02:52.204
I will not
fail to do my duty!

02:52.206 --> 02:53.872
Then we must begin at once.

02:53.874 --> 02:58.544
♪

02:58.546 --> 03:01.847
<i>(zap)</i>

03:01.849 --> 03:16.395
♪

03:18.398 --> 03:19.598
That can't be right.

03:19.600 --> 03:21.233
What can't be right?

03:21.235 --> 03:23.368
Nothing. Carry on.

03:45.592 --> 03:47.292
It is done.

03:48.795 --> 03:52.497
<i>(crickets)</i>

03:52.499 --> 03:53.899
<i>(snoring)</i>

03:56.769 --> 03:58.704
You weren't gone very long.

03:58.706 --> 04:01.006
Does that mean
everything's ok?

04:01.008 --> 04:02.841
Yup. Everything's fine.

04:02.843 --> 04:03.709
<i>(zap)</i>

04:03.711 --> 04:07.479
In that case, I'm
going back to bed.

04:07.481 --> 04:10.849
Sun's not up, then
neither am I.

04:10.851 --> 04:13.585
That's strange; the sun
should be up by now.

04:14.621 --> 04:16.421
The sun should be up by now!

04:18.658 --> 04:20.325
You can do this.

04:20.327 --> 04:29.668
<i>(buzzing)</i>

04:41.547 --> 04:45.317
Shining armor. Why, whatever
are you doing here?

04:45.319 --> 04:47.052
Back off, traitor.

04:47.054 --> 04:50.322
<i>Tirek: The only one discord</i>
<i>betrayed was himself.</i>

04:52.392 --> 04:55.327
Abandoning his true nature
to make "friends"

04:55.329 --> 04:58.430
With weak-minded equines
who offer him nothing.

05:10.743 --> 05:13.478
How could you do this?

05:15.948 --> 05:18.617
Why don't you go and
have a little fun?

05:18.619 --> 05:21.019
I won't stand in
your way.

05:21.021 --> 05:23.689
<i>(laugh)</i>

05:26.626 --> 05:29.394
<i>(heavy footsteps)</i>

05:29.396 --> 05:30.662
<i>(smash)</i>

05:37.537 --> 05:38.870
What have you done?

05:44.043 --> 05:46.845
Where is your magic?

05:49.015 --> 05:50.349
<i>(explosion)</i>

05:51.417 --> 05:52.951
I have to gain better control.

05:52.953 --> 05:54.619
I sure can't practice here.

05:55.621 --> 05:58.790
Twilight? Where are we going?

05:58.792 --> 06:00.659
Oh, uh, hi, spike.

06:00.661 --> 06:03.128
Gotta go...Somewhere else.

06:03.130 --> 06:04.396
<i>(whoosh)</i>

06:04.398 --> 06:05.664
Whoa!

06:08.601 --> 06:09.735
Whoa!

06:10.636 --> 06:11.770
Twilight?

06:15.541 --> 06:16.875
<i>(scream)</i>

06:16.877 --> 06:18.009
<i>(crash)</i>

06:19.746 --> 06:22.114
Oh my goodness. Are
you all right?

06:22.116 --> 06:23.982
Jumpin' June bugs,
twilight.

06:23.984 --> 06:26.151
When did you learn
to fly that fast?

06:26.153 --> 06:29.521
I must've caught a particularly
strong breeze...

06:29.523 --> 06:30.655
<i>(pop pop)</i>

06:30.657 --> 06:31.857
Or something.

06:31.859 --> 06:33.658
Must've been "or something"

06:33.660 --> 06:35.894
Because there wasn't
any breeze up there.

06:35.896 --> 06:39.731
But I don't really have time
to figure it out right now.

06:39.733 --> 06:44.136
Another visit to the castle of
the two sisters, I presume?

06:44.138 --> 06:45.904
We'd be more than
happy to accompany you.

06:45.906 --> 06:46.905
Not today.

06:46.907 --> 06:51.810
I need you all to stay here
and encourage everypony

06:51.812 --> 06:53.412
To remain inside.

07:02.655 --> 07:05.891
Getting rid of your magic so
that I cannot take it from you?

07:05.893 --> 07:07.526
That was your plan?

07:09.128 --> 07:11.129
How does it feel?

07:11.131 --> 07:14.433
Knowing that soon
every pegasus, unicorn,

07:14.435 --> 07:17.135
And earth pony will
bow to my will

07:17.137 --> 07:20.639
And that there is nothing
you can do to stop it.

07:20.641 --> 07:22.908
You will not prevail, tirek.

07:22.910 --> 07:26.044
Give my regards to cerberus.

07:31.184 --> 07:34.085
<i>Discord: You meant,</i>
<i>our will, didn't you?</i>

07:35.021 --> 07:36.688
Of course.

07:36.690 --> 07:39.124
Here. I want you to
have something.

07:39.126 --> 07:42.461
This was given to me by
someone very close to me.

07:42.463 --> 07:45.931
I give it to you as a sign
of my gratitude and loyalty.

07:45.933 --> 07:49.668
Oh my! I do love
a good accessory.

07:49.670 --> 07:52.103
I suppose that's
rarity's influence.

07:53.073 --> 07:57.609
Amusing. But we have no
time for such things.

07:57.611 --> 07:59.911
With the princesses out of
the way we can now--

08:01.681 --> 08:04.049
Is this meant to be humorous?

08:04.051 --> 08:05.183
Oh no!

08:05.185 --> 08:07.185
I haven't touched that one yet.

08:07.187 --> 08:08.653
There is a fourth?

08:08.655 --> 08:10.489
And you did not
tell me this?

08:10.491 --> 08:12.023
I just needed some assurance

08:12.025 --> 08:15.227
That you truly considered
this a team effort.

08:15.229 --> 08:17.629
And now I have it.

08:17.631 --> 08:20.699
Then where can we find
this fourth princess?

08:20.701 --> 08:22.133
Where is her castle?

08:22.135 --> 08:25.136
Castle? Oh. No.

08:25.138 --> 08:28.707
Princess twilight lives
above a library in ponyville.

08:28.709 --> 08:30.575
Castle. Ha ha!

08:32.111 --> 08:34.579
Not for much longer.

08:41.588 --> 08:46.224
<i>I think we've warned</i>
<i>everypony to stay inside.</i>

08:46.226 --> 08:48.693
I'm sure discord
will catch tirek

08:48.695 --> 08:50.629
And this will all be over soon.

08:50.631 --> 08:53.698
I'll bet he takes
his sweet time.

08:53.700 --> 08:56.668
<i>Discord: Or perhaps these</i>
<i>things just take time.</i>

08:56.670 --> 08:58.203
You're back!

08:58.205 --> 09:00.005
Did you bring the
cucumber sandwiches?

09:00.007 --> 09:05.710
I imagine they'll be your last
decent meal for quite some time.

09:05.712 --> 09:07.012
<i>(clang)</i>

09:07.647 --> 09:10.916
<i>(angry shouts)</i>

09:10.918 --> 09:12.250
Ta-da!

09:12.252 --> 09:13.919
You've gathered up all of them?

09:13.921 --> 09:16.187
And her little dragon, too.

09:16.189 --> 09:17.188
<i>(chomp)</i>

09:17.190 --> 09:18.924
Why are you doing this?

09:18.926 --> 09:20.892
I thought we were friends.

09:20.894 --> 09:25.664
But tirek offered me so much
more than just tea parties.

09:25.666 --> 09:27.198
Surely you saw this coming.

09:27.200 --> 09:30.235
I didn't. I really didn't.

09:40.246 --> 09:41.580
<i>(crash)</i>

09:45.251 --> 09:48.019
You really think she'd
do anything for them?

09:48.021 --> 09:51.957
If twilight has magic to
give, it will be yours.

09:51.959 --> 09:55.360
Soon there won't be a pegasus,
earth pony, or unicorn

09:55.362 --> 09:59.030
Who will be able to
stand up against us.

09:59.032 --> 10:03.268
Us? Who said
anything about us?

10:03.270 --> 10:04.603
You did.

10:05.171 --> 10:07.339
You've helped me grow strong.

10:07.341 --> 10:09.941
You've provided the means
by which I can obtain

10:09.943 --> 10:12.110
Princess twilight's magic.

10:12.112 --> 10:15.046
And now you are no
longer of any use to me.

10:24.156 --> 10:29.794
But you said this was a sign
of your gratitude and loyalty.

10:29.796 --> 10:32.697
A gift from someone
close to you.

10:32.699 --> 10:35.266
My brother who betrayed me.

10:35.268 --> 10:37.769
It is as worthless as he is.

10:40.339 --> 10:42.841
Surely you saw this coming.

10:42.843 --> 10:46.277
I didn't. I truly didn't.

10:51.951 --> 10:53.151
I can do this.

10:57.923 --> 11:00.759
See? Ha! Perfectly
controlled teleportation!

11:06.165 --> 11:07.298
<i>(groan)</i>

11:07.300 --> 11:09.367
<i>Tirek: Princess twilight!</i>

11:09.369 --> 11:11.136
(gasp) tirek!

11:11.138 --> 11:14.105
You have something
that belongs to me!

11:14.107 --> 11:15.240
<i>(explosion)</i>

11:15.741 --> 11:16.875
<i>(whoosh)</i>

11:21.347 --> 11:22.681
<i>(thud)</i>

11:27.787 --> 11:30.055
You're going to
give me what I want.

11:41.267 --> 11:42.734
<i>(explosion)</i>

11:42.736 --> 11:43.902
No!

11:46.172 --> 11:47.172
<i>(gasp)</i>

11:47.174 --> 11:49.908
<i>(crackling fire)</i>

11:58.884 --> 12:07.859
<i>(whoosh)</i>

12:07.861 --> 12:09.928
<i>(explosion)</i>

12:14.967 --> 12:18.403
Now I understand what your
fellow princesses have done.

12:22.308 --> 12:23.775
<i>(boom)</i>

12:29.782 --> 12:30.949
<i>(scream)</i>

12:35.054 --> 12:37.255
<i>(scream)</i>

12:37.257 --> 12:39.157
<i>(boom)</i>

12:39.159 --> 12:41.526
<i>(growl)</i>

12:42.361 --> 12:43.495
<i>(crash)</i>

12:44.096 --> 12:45.130
<i>(boom)</i>

12:45.132 --> 12:46.798
<i>(growl)</i>

12:54.006 --> 12:55.273
<i>(explosion)</i>

13:04.984 --> 13:06.117
<i>(explosion)</i>

13:07.353 --> 13:09.020
<i>(roar)</i>

13:17.563 --> 13:20.131
<i>(huge explosion)</i>

13:31.410 --> 13:34.279
It appears we are
at an impasse.

13:34.281 --> 13:36.548
How about a trade,
princess twilight?

13:39.485 --> 13:43.354
Their release for all the
alicorn magic in equestria.

13:43.356 --> 13:44.489
<i>(gasp)</i>

13:44.491 --> 13:48.326
<i>(shouts of protest)</i>

13:48.328 --> 13:51.462
What's it going to
be, princess?

13:55.902 --> 13:58.436
Rainbow dash: Don't
do it, twilight!

13:58.438 --> 14:00.071
We aren't worth it.

14:00.073 --> 14:02.173
<i>Discord: Oh, but you</i>
<i>are, fluttershy.</i>

14:02.175 --> 14:05.944
You're the pony who taught
me that friendship is magic.

14:05.946 --> 14:10.915
I had magic <i>and</i> friendship,
and now I don't have either.

14:10.917 --> 14:14.986
Enough! I want an answer.
And I want it now!

14:16.355 --> 14:27.966
♪

14:27.968 --> 14:32.237
I will give you my magic,
in exchange for my friends.

14:32.239 --> 14:33.504
<i>(all gasp)</i>

14:34.306 --> 14:36.040
As you wish.

14:43.616 --> 14:45.516
<i>All</i> of my friends.

14:45.518 --> 14:47.418
After the way he
has betrayed you,

14:47.420 --> 14:49.888
You still call him a "friend"?

14:50.456 --> 14:52.257
Release him!

14:52.259 --> 14:54.192
If that's what you want.

14:56.462 --> 14:58.496
Thank you, twilight.

14:58.498 --> 14:59.998
I'm sorry.

15:00.000 --> 15:01.165
I know.

15:01.167 --> 15:03.201
Your turn.

15:05.137 --> 15:12.443
<i>(cries of pain)</i>

15:16.682 --> 15:26.958
<i>(shouts)</i>

15:28.327 --> 15:31.429
Twilight, what
were you thinking?

15:31.431 --> 15:34.065
Tirek tricked me into believing
that he could offer me something

15:34.067 --> 15:36.134
More valuable than friendship.

15:36.136 --> 15:39.971
But there is nothing worth
more. I see that now.

15:39.973 --> 15:42.373
He lied when he said that
this medallion was given

15:42.375 --> 15:45.243
As a sign of gratitude
and loyalty.

15:45.245 --> 15:49.414
But when I say that it is a
sign of our true friendship,

15:49.416 --> 15:52.250
I am telling the truth.

15:56.188 --> 15:58.523
Do you think that might
be the last one we need?

15:58.525 --> 16:00.325
We have to get to the chest.

16:08.367 --> 16:10.668
<i>(whoosh)</i>

16:10.670 --> 16:17.976
♪

16:17.978 --> 16:19.110
<i>(heavy footstep)</i>

16:22.282 --> 16:25.316
I think we have to
do this together.

16:29.755 --> 16:31.055
<i>(amazed gasps)</i>

16:31.057 --> 16:41.265
♪

16:41.267 --> 17:11.329
♪

17:11.331 --> 17:12.630
<i>(snarl)</i>

17:16.735 --> 17:20.471
How is this possible?
You have no magic!

17:20.473 --> 17:22.073
You're wrong, tirek!

17:22.075 --> 17:24.275
I may have given you
my alicorn magic,

17:24.277 --> 17:27.478
But I carry within me the
most powerful magic of all!

17:32.117 --> 17:38.056
<i>(shouts of pain)</i>

17:43.128 --> 17:53.337
♪

17:53.339 --> 18:46.357
♪

18:46.359 --> 18:51.562
<i>(rumbling)</i>

18:51.564 --> 19:04.442
♪

19:04.444 --> 19:09.747
Sweet celestia! Are you all
seeing what I'm seeing?

19:09.749 --> 19:11.649
<i>Twilight: But whose is it?</i>

19:11.651 --> 19:14.619
I believe it is yours,
princess twilight.

19:16.488 --> 19:20.558
You've been wondering what you
are meant to do as a princess.

19:20.560 --> 19:22.360
Do you know now?

19:22.362 --> 19:25.329
As princess, I believe I
have the power to spread

19:25.331 --> 19:27.899
<i>The magic of friendship</i>
<i>across equestria.</i>

19:27.901 --> 19:30.635
<i>That is the role I am meant</i>
<i>to have in our world.</i>

19:30.637 --> 19:32.637
The role I choose to have.

19:32.639 --> 19:35.373
But I didn't defeat
tirek on my own.

19:35.375 --> 19:37.608
It took all of us
to unlock the chest.

19:37.610 --> 19:39.243
Then it is unlikely
you are meant

19:39.245 --> 19:41.312
To take on this
task alone.

19:41.314 --> 19:43.447
All: Oooh! Wow!

19:43.449 --> 19:47.852
<i>You are now twilight sparkle,</i>
<i>the princess of friendship.</i>

19:52.457 --> 19:56.561
But what is the princess of
friendship without her friends?

20:05.904 --> 20:08.940
Wait a minute.
Where's my throne?

20:08.942 --> 20:11.275
I don't think you're
quite there yet.

20:11.277 --> 20:14.345
Yes, well, I suppose not.

20:16.381 --> 20:23.621
<i>♪ upbeat</i>

20:23.623 --> 20:26.791
<i>♪ each one of us has</i>
<i>something special ♪</i>

20:26.793 --> 20:31.262
<i>♪ that makes us different</i>
<i>that makes us rare ♪</i>

20:31.264 --> 20:34.432
<i>♪ we have a light that</i>
<i>shines within us ♪</i>

20:34.434 --> 20:39.370
<i>♪ that we were always</i>
<i>meant to share ♪</i>

20:39.372 --> 20:41.305
<i>♪ and when we come together</i>

20:41.307 --> 20:43.007
<i>♪ combine the light</i>
<i>that shines within ♪</i>

20:43.009 --> 20:44.909
♪ there is nothing we can't do

20:44.911 --> 20:46.877
<i>♪ there is no battle</i>
<i>we can't win ♪</i>

20:46.879 --> 20:50.681
<i>♪ there'll be a star</i>
<i>to guide the way ♪</i>

20:50.683 --> 20:53.317
<i>♪ it's inside us every day</i>

20:53.319 --> 20:57.255
<i>♪ see it now! See it now!</i>

20:57.257 --> 21:00.825
<i>♪ let the rainbow remind you</i>

21:00.827 --> 21:04.562
<i>♪ that together we</i>
<i>will always shine ♪</i>

21:04.564 --> 21:08.266
<i>♪ let the rainbow remind you</i>

21:08.268 --> 21:11.602
<i>♪ that forever this</i>
<i>will be our time ♪</i>

21:11.604 --> 21:19.710
♪

21:19.712 --> 21:23.347
<i>♪ let the rainbow remind you</i>

21:23.349 --> 21:28.486
<i>♪ that together we</i>
<i>will always shine ♪</i>

21:31.490 --> 21:41.699
♪

21:41.701 --> 21:55.646
♪
